-- Ascent Media Buys Monitronics International in Deal Valued at $1.2 Billion
-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 2010-12-17T22:53:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-17/ascent-media-buys-monitronics-international-in-deal-valued-at-1-2-billion.html
Ascent Media Corp. acquired
Monitronics International Inc. in a transaction valued at about
$1.2 billion, including liabilities like the assumption of
existing structured financing.  Ascent said the acquisition will be funded with $413
million in cash and $105 million in debt from a new $175 million
credit facility.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  